title: CSI ETABS Version 16.0.0 Build 1488
description:
CSI ETABS Version 16.0.0 with Keygen/License Generator by LAVteam (Thanks!)

1. Disconnect from the Internet
2. Run Setup 32 or 64 bit (your preferred)
3. Run the Etabs_2016_v16_kg and in the keygen folder it will be generated a lservrc license file (~4KB)
4. Copy the license file to :
a. For 32bit Windows : C:Program Files (x86)Computers and StructuresETABS 2016 and C:Program Files (x86)Computers and StructuresETABS 2016CSiLicensing
b. For 64bit Windows : C:Program FilesComputers and StructuresETABS 2016 and C:Program FilesComputers and StructuresETABS 2015CSiLicensing
c. For another user-chosen folder, find the directory and copy the license file there.
5. Ignore the "Unregistered". Program will run fine unless you connect to the internet without blocking at the firewall.
6. Make sure ETABS.exe is blocked at the Firewall from connecting to the Internet

The How-to-crack above works. If the error "...license file missing etc etc" repeat the step above
License is valid for 355 days starting from 28/08/2016 (ends somewhere in August 2017). If you want this time not to end :
1. Change time at your windows clock and put it some years before 2016
2. Wait for the next CSI ETABS update (Version 17 or 16.x.x) coming in the beggining of year 2017 (or earlier 2016) or another crack.
Until then support by keeping this torrent alive by seeding it or adding it to a seedbox, trust me it's worth the share!
